{"title":"HTB Popcorn","uid":"11c79fec8a41036689b6be063d1dcd0c","slug":"Virtual Attack[17]","date":"2022-12-16T14:18:00.000Z","updated":"2024-03-13T00:55:14.620Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Virtual Attack[17].json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"Port-Scan\"><a href=\"#Port-Scan\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Port Scan\"></a>Port Scan</h2><p><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/Fr6nm23kMKblmVQ3JDmsjqhrxiW1.png\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h2 id=\"Web-Contents-Discovery\"><a href=\"#Web-Contents-Discovery\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Web Contents Discovery\"></a>Web Contents Discovery</h2><p><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FifzO5xz1VpbQkdgalI00ObPo4Sy.png\"><br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/Ft1jnpuHX8f45m1Zu1YvZx2SL_hi.png\"><br>Also we find the another content <code>/reanme</code>, <code>/torrent</code></p>\n<p>When we visit the <code>test.php</code>.<br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/Fh5KWBLQCnE2uci-V72v17q8cbAA.png\"></p>\n<p>We visit the <code>/torrent</code> content, we found we can upload the specific <code>torrent</code> file.<br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FnoE9DF9uflMDvMdTzU_aBNw_K1f.png\"><br>I try to modify the torrent file like adding some malicious commands in it, but it failed.<br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/Fsb3cZ1K6qmnj7hrIu1SknzJ-VVG.png\"></p>\n<p>But we can upload the screenshots in my uploaded torrent file.<br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FsB1ShbVgmk59A7Y5dtHAXNl2ge-.png\"></p>\n<p>We can upload the images with mailcious php commands, and <code>/rename</code>the image file name.<br>So we can visit the php page and get a <code>www-data</code> shell.<br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FvcZTHrUQusyaeUqwyPWRkn3EEjx.png\"></p>\n<p>We can enter any command to control the machine.<br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FjvuzViTMKV3oEPSQXbGTHL1IDct.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/Fh830DCWz4E54ZxGlP4cwLeTMsrM.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"Privilege-escalation\"><a href=\"#Privilege-escalation\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Privilege escalation\"></a>Privilege escalation</h2><p>We find a suspicious file in <code>/home/george</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-latex\" data-language=\"latex\"><code class=\"language-latex\">/home/george/.cache/motd.legal-displayed<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FmszyV4AvHNaRoL7rUVN8Q21mm1y.png\"></p>\n<p>I googling <code>MOTD Exploitation</code>, here what I found.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14339\">https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14339</a><br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FtFgjxlMYuDhho1wfZsC86xTSdfH.png\"></p>\n<p>We copy the exp.sh from <code>exploit database</code>, and run it. We can get the root shell.<br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FoleNiRAOkX8-ehBzSqppaduiqAP.png\"></p>\n","text":"Port Scan Web Contents DiscoveryAlso we find the another content /reanme, /torrent When we visit the test.php. We visit the /torrent content...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":814,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Penetration Test","slug":"Penetration-Test","count":20,"path":"api/categories/Penetration-Test.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hack the Box","slug":"Hack-the-Box","count":10,"path":"api/tags/Hack-the-Box.json"},{"name":"Penestration Test","slug":"Penestration-Test","count":6,"path":"api/tags/Penestration-Test.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link